Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:42.60,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:46.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
